\ip To we Yoęž‰n e saęž‰saęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu nowoęž‰, ene wiyoęž‰ Gaius, emoęž‰ iligaęž‰foęž‰. Gaius eyoęž‰ Keliso kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ asuwaęž‰taęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, Yoęž‰n eyoęž‰ Gaius emoęž‰woęž‰ sagalaki, moęž‰foęž‰s we aęž‰na saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Diotefaęž‰s ene man dimidab aęž‰noęž‰ Gaius e moęž‰kudu hamanaęž‰ki, Yoęž‰n eyoęž‰ hagugoęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ emoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰foęž‰.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 1.1 \xt Ilig 19.29, Lom 16.23\x*Misaęž‰ kalu saęž‰s amiloęž‰ dowoęž‰woęž‰ ne koęž‰loęž‰, niyoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s we ne milile Gaius gemoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰l. Niyoęž‰ gemoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ hendele disaęž‰.   
\p
\v 2 Ne milile, ge Gode oęž‰liaęž‰loęž‰ ege dowoęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ ge asuwaęž‰talikiyoęž‰, gi doęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ halaidoęž‰ domaęž‰ki, niyoęž‰ ge Godemoęž‰ dulugu soęž‰loęž‰l.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 1.3 \xt 2Yoęž‰n 1.4\x*Keliso kalu i noloęž‰ neloęž‰wa faęž‰laęž‰dotaęž‰gaęž‰, nemoęž‰ saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ to hendeleyoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ tilidaęž‰daki, to hendele aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab, aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ sioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ ne mada sagaloęž‰.  
\v 4 Ni soęž‰wa iyoęž‰ to hendeleyoęž‰ kudu haęž‰nab aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ ne daęž‰dakiyoęž‰, mada alan sagalaęž‰sen. Sagaloęž‰ niloęž‰ wemaęž‰yoęž‰, sagalan noloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ tininilaęž‰.   
\p
\v 5 Ni mili, giyoęž‰ magesoęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ tili dofoęž‰lalikiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ to nafa aęž‰noęž‰ hendele kudu haęž‰naęž‰lab. Kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ ge tamin amioęž‰ moęž‰baęž‰baęž‰ koęž‰sega, giyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ tili dofoęž‰lab.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1.6 \xt Tait 3.13\x*Magesoęž‰ kalu i aęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ yaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, giloęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰sen man aęž‰noęž‰ iliyoęž‰ saęž‰s kalukaęž‰isale nolboęž‰woęž‰ maloloęž‰ me. Magesoęž‰ noloęž‰ geloęž‰ amioęž‰ waęž‰ka yaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ haęž‰nab amioęž‰, gioęž‰ Godeloęž‰ sagalemaęž‰noęž‰ man oęž‰ngoęž‰ dimidaki, iyoęž‰ asuwaęž‰taęž‰bi.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1.7 \xt 1Kol 9.11-12\x*Moęž‰woęž‰ iyoęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ wiya iliki walamaęž‰ni haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, haęž‰laęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale iya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ nowoęž‰ moęž‰diaęž‰sen.  
\v 8 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ niliyoęž‰ asuwaęž‰faęž‰niki. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, iliyoęž‰ to hendele widalikiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ ua iliki dimidamaęž‰noęž‰. \fig Kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ dinafa tilidowaęž‰bi.|alt="Enjoying a meal together" src="11_1Ki_01_02_RG_gr.tif" size="col" copy="Â© Sweet Publishing http://sweetpublishing.com, licensed under a CC: BY-SA 3.0 Unported licence." ref="1.5" \fig*   
\p
\v 9 Niyoęž‰ to noloęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰sa saęž‰saęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, saęž‰s kalukaęž‰isalemoęž‰woęž‰ iligaęž‰foęž‰. Koęž‰sega Diotefaęž‰s, e saęž‰s usamiloęž‰ misaęž‰ kalu domaęž‰noęž‰ asulaki kailakiyoęž‰, nililoęž‰ to sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ eyoęž‰ moęž‰daęž‰dab.  
\v 10 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ne giloęž‰wa yakiyoęž‰, eloęž‰ ni sadaęž‰dakiloęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ kalaba saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰. Man mogagoęž‰ eloęž‰ dimidaęž‰senoęž‰ imilig koęž‰mba. Keliso magesoęž‰ kalu nol eloęž‰ amiloęž‰ yab aęž‰noęž‰, eyoęž‰ moęž‰tili domaęž‰noęž‰ asuloęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, Keliso kalu nolbaęž‰yoęž‰ magesoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ tilidomaęž‰noęž‰ asulabikiyoęž‰, eyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Keliso aęž‰noęž‰ saęž‰s usamioęž‰ dowabenaęž‰ki oęž‰lugaęž‰felaęž‰sen.   
\p
\v 11 \x - \xo 1.11 \xt 1Yoęž‰n 3.6-10\x*Ni milile, giyoęž‰ man mogagoęž‰woęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰soęž‰bo. Koęž‰sega man nafale dimidaęž‰bi. Kalu abeyoęž‰ man digaloęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, Gode Enoęž‰. Kalu abeyoęž‰ man mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, e Godeyoęž‰ moęž‰asuloęž‰.  
\v 12 Demitius eloęž‰ dimidan aęž‰noęž‰ nafa dimidaęž‰len aęž‰laęž‰liki tambowaęž‰yoęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ to hendele aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ imilab. Nioęž‰ hendele saęž‰laboęž‰loęž‰b aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ giliyoęž‰ asulab koęž‰loęž‰, niliyoęž‰loęž‰ eloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ nafale aęž‰laęž‰asulaki sioęž‰.   
\p
\v 13 \x - \xo 1.13 \xt 2Yoęž‰n 1.12\x*Niyoęž‰ towoęž‰ modoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ gimoęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰ asuloęž‰l koęž‰sega, niyoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s amioęž‰ moęž‰saęž‰saęž‰limaęž‰noęž‰.  
\v 14 Ne giloęž‰ amioęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ma miaęž‰noęž‰ asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ ne yakiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ migi kudu saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰.   
\p
\v 15 Giyoęž‰ haęž‰sa taęž‰biyoęž‰. Gi mili wiloęž‰ sab wemaęž‰yoęž‰ sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ gimoęž‰ sagaęž‰tab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ni sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ ne mili konamiloęž‰ sab imoęž‰woęž‰ tambo saęž‰laęž‰biyoęž‰.   